    "The LLM was capable of processing and reviewing the entire dataset of 50 papers in a fraction of the time required by human reviewers, demonstrating a high level of scalability that could greatly benefit systematic literature reviews, especially in fields with rapidly expanding bodies of work.",
    "Additionally, the consistent format and structure of the LLM-generated reviews suggest that Mistral LLM can provide a standardized approach to literature review, potentially streamlining the integration of findings across multiple studies.",
